ing to regulatory calls.In the past few years, Gitzo has continuously carried out all-round and diversified financial knowledge popularization activities for young people including college students, and has imperceptibly guided the consumption needs of young people through various forms such as launching innovation practice competitions in cooperation with top domestic universities, helping them establish rational consumption concepts and rationally plan consumption needs.In order to help them accumulate wealth in life. On the occasion of the arrival of the 12th, Gitzo reminds all consumers to establish a reasonable sense of consumption and a correct view of money, resist blind consumption and excessive consumption, and avoid consumer lending errors, so as not to affect personal credit and future economic life. In the future, Gitzo will continue to rely on its mature and reliable consumer financial system and constantly updated and iterative financial products.It provides consumers with more demand-oriented and diversified services, continuously assists the public to improve their financial knowledge level, helps consumers cultivate the concept of rational consumption and moderate borrowing, and becomes a reliable consumer financial partner for consumers throughout their lives.
